title: #146: The Life and Crimes of George HW Bush with  Gordon Rochford
description:
Thank you for tuning in for another episode of Tin Foil Hat with Sam Tripoli. This episode we welcome from Those Conspiracy Guys podcast, Gordon Rochford, to talk about the life and crimes of the 41st President! Thank you so much for your support. Please check out....
